\begin_layout Section
协变矢量逆变矢量
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
假设
\begin_inset Formula $x_{\mu}$
\end_inset

的变换为：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
x_{\mu}^{\prime}=\Lambda_{\mu}^{\phantom{\mu}\nu}x_{\nu}
\]

\end_inset

那么逆变换的矩阵为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
x_{\mu}=\Lambda_{\mu}^{-1,\nu}x_{\nu}^{\prime}
\]

\end_inset

洛伦兹矩阵的逆矩阵相当于里面的速度
\begin_inset Formula $v$
\end_inset

变成
\begin_inset Formula $-v$
\end_inset

，也就是空间部分反号。按照通常的符号约定，空间部分反号相当于改变指标的上下位置。上指标的四矢量变换为：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
x^{\prime\mu}=\Lambda_{\phantom{\mu}\nu}^{\mu}x^{\nu}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $\Lambda_{\phantom{\mu}\nu}^{\mu}$
\end_inset

就相当于
\begin_inset Formula $\Lambda_{\mu}^{\phantom{\mu}\nu}$
\end_inset

的逆矩阵。所以将指标在上的矢量称为逆变矢量，因为它们是按照逆矩阵变换的。当然，正逆是相对的，我们习惯上这么约定。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
当坐标的变换为
\begin_inset Formula $x^{\prime\mu}=\Lambda_{\phantom{\mu}\nu}^{\mu}x^{\nu}$
\end_inset

时，根据求导的链式规则：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\frac{\partial}{\partial x^{\mu}}f\left(x^{\prime}\right) & =\Lambda_{\phantom{\mu}\nu}^{\mu}\frac{\partial}{\partial x^{\prime\mu}}f\left(x^{\prime}\right)\\
\frac{\partial}{\partial x^{\prime\mu}}f\left(x^{\prime}\right) & =\Lambda_{-1,\nu}^{\mu}\frac{\partial}{\partial x^{\mu}}f\left(x^{\prime}\right)
\end{align*}

\end_inset

对比一下：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
x^{\prime\mu} & =\Lambda_{\phantom{\mu}\nu}^{\mu}x^{\nu}\\
\frac{\partial}{\partial x^{\prime\mu}} & =\Lambda_{-1,\nu}^{\mu}\frac{\partial}{\partial x^{\mu}}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

也就是对逆变矢量的偏导数，是按照协变的洛伦兹矩阵变换的。按照我们的约定，协变矢量的指标在下，所以我们定义：
\color blue

\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\partial_{\mu}=\frac{\partial}{\partial x^{\mu}}=\left(\partial_{t},\nabla\right)
\]

\end_inset

注意，与通常的协变矢量相比，
\begin_inset Formula $\partial_{\mu}$
\end_inset

的空间部分是没有负号的。所以
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\partial_{\mu}J^{\mu}=\partial_{t}J^{0}+\nabla\cdot\sbf J=0.
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

